#### Team-Specific Code Style Preferences ####

# Naming Conventions for Common Scenarios
# Note: These are guidance for developers and Copilot.
# EditorConfig cannot enforce variable names in lambdas/loops programmatically,
# but this documents team preferences.

# Lambda parameter preferences:
# ✅ Preferred: .FirstOrDefault(p => p.Name == "Jeremy")
# ✅ Alternative: Use descriptive names for complex lambdas (e.g., user => user.IsActive)
# ❌ Avoid: Single letters other than 'p' for simple predicates

# ForEach loop variable preferences:
# ✅ Preferred: foreach (var item in collection)
# ✅ Nested loops: foreach (var outerItem in outer) { foreach (var innerItem in inner) }
# ❌ Avoid: Generic names like 'i', 'x', 'obj' unless absolutely clear from context

